e thermal pressure balances the vertical gravitational field\ncaptures better the shape of the $\\Sigma_{\\rm SFR}-\\Sigma_{\\rm gas}$\nrelationship. However, such models fail to reproduce the data completely,\nsuggesting that thermal pressure plays an important role in the disks of dwarf\ngalaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 May 2018 03:42:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-06"}
