 is therefore\nto provide a review of proofs of classical regret bounds for index-based\nstrategies for $K$-armed stochastic bandits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 May 2018 09:05:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2019 15:13:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 1 Jul 2022 10:12:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-04"}
