ll injury\nprovides an improved quantitative framework for understanding cell death and\nrecovery and lays a foundation for developing effective therapeutics for acute\ninjury.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 May 2018 15:51:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Oct 2019 23:47:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-25"}
